  "texts": [
    "Disagreements were resolved by judgment of a third reviewer (JNK).",
    "Overlap of guideline content was visualized using pyCirclize 14.",
    "Items recommended by at least 50% of all reporting guidelines or 50% of reporting guidelines with a specified systematic development process (i.e., comprehensive consensus) were considered universal recommendations for clinical AI research reporting.",
    "This systematic review was registered at OSF https://doi.org/10.17605/OSF.",
    "IO/YZE6J on August 25, 2023."
  ]
